Spray cold grill and utensils well with cooking spray. Position grill 3 to 4 inches from heat. Heat grill according to manufacturer's suggestion. Make glaze: stir together spreadable fruit, mustard, and onion. Place ham steaks on grate and grill 2 minutes. Turn steaks over, lightly brush with glaze, and grill 2 minutes. Turn steaks again, brush with remaining glaze and grill 2 minutes or until done.